      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ECO FORCE (3) has had a few chances but is racing well and finds a nice race. Third to Fundamental Nature & Torsheen two back is excellent form for this, 1400m probably a slight bridge too far last time. This looks easier and she gets every chance from a nice gate back 100m in trip. LADY SADLER (6) resumes. She only managed one run last time in when a distant second to a potentially very good horse in Tennessee Bound here. She maps well and has winning claims. FEROCIOUS FRANKIE (5) struggled here fresh, any extra ground should suit. HEAVENLY KISS (1) will be rock-hard fit now following a nice effort at Wagga last start when fifth. Looks a strong place chance.",
